This manual covers the installation and day to day use of
      &subproject.this.name; &subproject.this.version;.



&subproject.this.name; is a storage mechanism for audio
      files, and is one of the components of &project.nametag;, a
      complete audio player for home use.


The latest version of this document is always available
      from the &project.website;.




